Burger Website
A simple website template for a burger restaurant.

Table of Contents
Introduction
Features
Usage
Responsive Design
Contributing
License
Introduction
This is a basic website template designed for a burger restaurant. It features a modern and responsive design, allowing users to navigate through different sections of the website easily.

Features
Clean and attractive user interface.
Responsive design for optimal viewing on various devices.
Navigation menu for easy access to different sections of the website.
Eye-catching animations and effects to enhance user experience.
Usage
To use the website template, simply download or clone the repository to your local machine. You can then customize the content, images, and styles according to your preferences.

HTML Structure
The HTML file (index.html) contains the structure of the website, including header, navigation menu, sections for home, menu, specials, and contact.

CSS Styling
The CSS styles are defined in the Burger.css file, providing the visual appearance and layout of the website.

JavaScript
There is currently no JavaScript functionality implemented in this version of the website.

Responsive Design
The website template is designed to be responsive, ensuring optimal viewing experience across a wide range of devices, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones.

Contributing
Contributions are welcome! If you find any bugs or have suggestions for improvements, please feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request.
